Norwegian sub-areas (lokasjon) for commercial fishing

Source: R/datasets-docs.R
fdir_sub_areas.Rd

Norwegian sub-areas (lokasjon) for commercial fishing

Usage

fdir_sub_areas

Format

sf object in decimal degrees (EPSG:4326) containing major fishing zones defined by the Norwegian Directorate of Fisheries.

Source

Norwegian Directorate of Fisheries

See also

Other datasets: fdir_main_areas, ices_areas

Examples

# \donttest{
basemap(fdir_sub_areas) + 
annotation_spatial(fdir_sub_areas, fill = NA)

# }
